{"word":"G5241 - ὑπερεντυγχάνω - hyperentynchánō - hoop-er-en-toong-khan'-o - Make intercession for","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερεντυγχάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hyperentynchánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er-en-toong-khan'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make intercession for</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேண்டுதல் செய்"},{"paragraph":"to intercede for one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G1793 - ἐντυγχάνω - entynchánō - en-toong-khan'-o/1793\">G1793</a>; to <i>intercede in behalf of:</i> - make intercession for.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1783/1783\">G1783</a>, <a href=\"#/G1793/1793\">G1793</a>, <a href=\"#/G5177/5177\">G5177</a>, <a href=\"#/G5241/5241\">G5241</a>"}]}